        <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>Render the UI. This is repeated for each viewport.
Here you can either render immediately, or insert a task into `params.tasks`, which get Z-sorted.
* `params` will remain alive as long as the tasks are used.
* You&apos;ll have at most one living task at a time, so you can write a non-owning pointer to an internal task.
</verbatim> </para>
